      description: 'A comprehensive legal and regulatory guide for value-based care. Covers the fundamental tension between VBC collaboration requirements and federal fraud and abuse laws, the landmark 2020 Stark and Anti-Kickback regulatory modernization with three-tiered safe harbors, HIPAA data sharing requirements for population health, CMS audit preparedness and OIG enforcement trends, and state-level regulatory considerations. Essential viewing for compliance officers, healthcare attorneys, and executives designing VBC arrangements.'
